wikipedia_page.main: Elizabeth Louise "Beth" Storry (born 24 April 1978) is an English field hockey goalkeeper. She was part of the British teams that won the bronze medal at the 2012 Olympics and placed sixth in 2008.Storry is lesbian. She lives with her partner in Utrecht and works as a business manager with Nike, Inc. She is an accomplished baker, and in 2014 appeared in the Dutch version of The Great British Bake Off TV show, Heel Holland Bakt.
